# Mail — <%= appName %>

Email delivery via Nodemailer.

## Environment

See `.env.example` for `MAIL_PROVIDER=<%= provider %>` settings.

## Usage

```typescript
import { mail } from './src/services/mail/index.js';

await mail.send({
  to: 'user@example.com',
  subject: 'Welcome',
  html: '<p>Welcome to <%= appName %></p>',
});
```

Supported providers: `smtp`, `sendgrid`, `mailgun`
